{"id":400,"date":"2020-10-12T16:38:58","date_gmt":"2020-10-12T14:38:58","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/xanasoft.com\/?page_id=400"},"modified":"2023-10-15T11:24:43","modified_gmt":"2023-10-15T11:24:43","slug":"notifydirectdiskaccess","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/sandboxie-plus.com\/sandboxie\/notifydirectdiskaccess\/","title":{"rendered":"Notify Direct Disk Access"},"content":{"rendered":"<h1>Notify Direct Disk Access<\/h1>\n<p><em>NotifyDirectDiskAccess<\/em> is a sandbox setting in <a href=\"SandboxieIni\">Sandboxie Ini<\/a>. It is typically specified as <em>NotifyDirectDiskAccess=y<\/em>.<\/p>\n<p>Usage:<\/p>\n<pre><code>   .\n   .\n   .\n   [DefaultBox]\n   NotifyDirectDiskAccess=y<\/code><\/pre>\n<p>Note that the default behavior of Sandboxie is to deny all direct access requests, unless explicit direct access is given to the hard disk device through the <a href=\"OpenFilePath\">OpenFilePath<\/a> or <a href=\"OpenPipePath\">OpenPipePath<\/a> settings. Normally, a message is not issued when such access is denied.<\/p>\n<p>This setting can not be altered using <a href=\"SandboxieControl\">Sandboxie Control<\/a> and must be edited in <a href=\"SandboxieIni\">Sandboxie Ini<\/a>.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Notify Direct Disk Access NotifyDirectDiskAccess is a sandbox setting in Sandboxie Ini. It is typically specified as NotifyDirectDiskAccess=y. Usage: . . . [DefaultBox] NotifyDirectDiskAccess=y Note that the default behavior of Sandboxie is to deny all direct access requests, unless explicit direct access is given to the hard disk device through the OpenFilePath or OpenPipePath settings. &hellip; <a href=\"https:\/\/sandboxie-plus.com\/sandboxie\/notifydirectdiskaccess\/\" class=\"more-link\">Continue reading <span class=\"screen-reader-text\">Notify Direct Disk Access<\/span> <span class=\"meta-nav\">&rarr;<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":108,"menu_order":0,"comment_stat